<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08037f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08037f">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08037f"> 37(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> London talks to Africa</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>&ldquo;Wandering voices&rdquo;</b> On Saturday last <mark>a programme sent out from London was &ldquo;picked up&rdquo; at Middelburg, in South Africa</mark>. During the course of this programme the London station &ldquo;picked up&rdquo; station K.D.K.A., Pittsburg and &ldquo;relaid&rdquo; its message, with the result that the strains of an American concert were heard at Middelburg. <small> <a name="IT2jan24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#IT2jan24"><cite title="source">Irish Times</cite></a> (2 January 1924) 4/4</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
